      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey monday community <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/waving_hand.png?v=15\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>spot-nik, the makers of best-selling apps SuperForm and SuperMail, is excited to announce the launch of <strong>SuperPlanner,</strong> a new app for resource management and capacity planning inside <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p>With SuperPlanner you can:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/glowing_star.png?v=15\" title=\":glowing_star:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":glowing_star:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> See real-time workload and capacity<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/glowing_star.png?v=15\" title=\":glowing_star:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":glowing_star:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Assign tasks by skills and roles<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/glowing_star.png?v=15\" title=\":glowing_star:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":glowing_star:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Account for PTO and holidays<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/glowing_star.png?v=15\" title=\":glowing_star:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":glowing_star:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Prevent overallocation and missed deadlines with smarter planning</p>\n<p>SuperPlanner is now live in the <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> Marketplace.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_down.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Try it for free and let us know what you think! <a href=\"https://spotnik.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?oauth_payload_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjbGllbnRfaWQiOiJhNzIzOTcwMTY5NTRhYTMzZTI3MjkzNjk4ODU2NjE0MiIsInJlc3BvbnNlX3R5cGUiOiJpbnN0YWxsIiwib2F1dGhfdmVyc2lvbiI6Mn0.eGPbuOUZKO_cNMNRTmclD68d2LE9teDu8smkFV58cGo\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com: Where Teams Get Work Done</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/laptop.png?v=15\" title=\":laptop:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":laptop:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Learn more here - <a href=\"https://spot-nik.com/product/superplanner/\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Resource planning made easier in monday.com | SuperPlanner</a></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/a/6a767a697aab8d511df674d617a9528791dfff59.jpeg\" title=\"ChatGPT Image Feb 11, 2026, 11_09_31 AM\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/a/6a767a697aab8d511df674d617a9528791dfff59_2_500x500.jpeg\" alt=\"ChatGPT Image Feb 11, 2026, 11_09_31 AM\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">ChatGPT Image Feb 11, 2026, 11_09_31 AM</span><span class=\"informations\">1024×1024 128 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
